author: smuzaffar
body:
LTO build complains that `struct MTDHit` is defined multiple time in the package

- https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/blob/master/Validation/MtdValidation/plugins/BtlSimHitsValidation.cc#L42-L48
- https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/blob/master/Validation/MtdValidation/plugins/BtlLocalRecoValidation.cc#L45-L51

This PR proposes to change the name of one of these.
title: [LTO] Fix ODR warnings for Validation/MtdValidation
